.TH "RK_TMUX_BELL Reference" "" "" ""
.PP
\f[CR]tmux\f[R] shows a \f[CR]!\f[R] next to a window in the current
session if a pane in that window triggers a bell.
.PP
Do \f[CR]sleep 5; printf \(aq\(rsa\(aq\f[R] in a pane to test a bell.
.PP
Note that \f[CR]tmux\f[R] does not notify for bells in other sessions,
and the terminal client also won\(cqt get notifications of bells in
other sessions.
